OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy fog and frost will soon
OL,6,Fclear to leave some dry weather this
OL,7,Fmorning with sunny spells. However,
OL,8,Fcloud will gradually increase and a
OL,9,Fscattering of showers are likely to
OL,10,Fdevelop by the afternoon. A gentle
OL,11,Feasterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers easing this evening
OL,14,Fto leave a mostly dry night with clear
OL,15,Fspells. However, the odd shower could
OL,16,Freturn later. Becoming breezy, though
OL,17,Fa patchy frost is still expected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
