OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FThere'll be bright spells and
OL,6,Fone or two showers on Tuesday morning.
OL,7,FA mostly fine afternoon should follow
OL,8,Fwith sunny spells. Pleasant in the
OL,9,Fsunshine, though a cooling breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,12,FLargely dry during the remainder of
OL,13,Fthe week, with high pressure giving
OL,14,Fgenerally settled weather. Some warm
OL,15,Fsunshine, though breezy at first, and
OL,16,Fsome patchy overnight frosts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
